---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Container from '../components/Container.astro';
import SectionTitle from '../components/SectionTitle.astro';
import { withBasePath } from '../i18n';
---
<BaseLayout title="奉献" description="支持我们在 Agape Triangle 的使命">
  <Container class="py-14 sm:py-20">
    <SectionTitle eyebrow="GIVE" title="支持我们在 Agape Triangle 的使命" subtitle="谢谢你与我们同工，一同推进福音事工。" />

    <div class="mx-auto mt-12 grid max-w-5xl gap-6 lg:grid-cols-2">
      <section class="rounded-3xl border border-black/10 bg-white/40 p-7 shadow-soft">
        <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl text-ink-950">奉献说明</h3>
        <img
          src={withBasePath('/images/zelle.png')}
          alt="Zelle"
          class="mt-5 w-full rounded-2xl object-contain ring-1 ring-black/10 bg-white p-4"
          loading="lazy"
        />
        <div class="mt-5 rounded-2xl border border-black/5 bg-parchment-50 p-5">
          <div class="text-sm font-medium text-ink-950">Zelle 收款信息</div>
          <div class="mt-2 text-sm leading-7 text-ink-900/70">
            <div>收款人：<span class="font-medium text-ink-950">AGAPE TRIANGLE CHINESE CHURCH</span></div>
            <div>邮箱：<a href="mailto:ruthzyn@outlook.com" class="font-medium text-cinnabar-600 underline decoration-cinnabar-300 underline-offset-4">ruthzyn@outlook.com</a></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-4 text-sm leading-7 text-ink-900/70">
          <p>您可以通过以下方式使用 Zelle 奉献：</p>
          <ol class="mt-2 list-decimal space-y-1 pl-5">
            <li>打开您的银行 App，找到 Zelle 转账功能</li>
            <li>用银行 App 扫描上方二维码，或手动输入上方邮箱地址</li>
            <li>输入奉献金额并发送</li>
          </ol>
          <p class="mt-3">如有其他奉献方式需求，请联系我们。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-6">
          <a href={withBasePath('/contact')} class="rounded-full border border-black/10 bg-white/40 px-6 py-3 text-center text-sm font-medium text-ink-950 transition hover:bg-white/70">咨询奉献方式</a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="rounded-3xl border border-black/10 bg-white/40 p-7 shadow-soft">
        <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl text-ink-950">奉献用途（示例）</h3>
        <ul class="mt-5 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-sm leading-7 text-ink-900/70">
          <li>本地宣教与福音外展</li>
          <li>主日与团契聚会支持</li>
          <li>关怀与牧养事工</li>
          <li>场地与行政开销</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </div>
  </Container>
</BaseLayout>
